{"tid":594022,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASRock 進軍VGA卡市場！主力推出AMD卡！","createTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T07:19:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84dd3005d5ed468c6a0e7bc79199745c10fef38d","tid":594022,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"ASRock 將推出基於 AMD Radeon 的繪圖卡，有望最快在今年第二季推出市場。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，ASRock 推出的繪圖卡將會採用較簡約的設計，並且專門用於採礦，類似其他 AIB 插件板合作夥伴一樣，可以從一些參考設計卡開始，然後推出定制的繪圖卡。近年，加密貨幣挖掘熱潮興起，ASRock 在去年已推出專為「掘礦」市場而設的主機板，加上其多年的經驗，相信在開拓 AMD Radeon 繪圖卡市場有一定的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/16438/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%8D%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4_ASRock_%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%96%BC_AMD_Radeon_%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%8D%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F16438%2F%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4_ASRock_%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2596%25BC_AMD_Radeon_%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%258D%25A1&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ce7b9d3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/16438/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%8D%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4_ASRock_%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%96%BC_AMD_Radeon_%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%8D%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videocardz.com/newz/asrock-to-enter-graphics-cards-market\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideocardz.com%2Fnewz%2Fasrock-to-enter-graphics-cards-market&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9b603ad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://videocardz.com/newz/asrock-to-enter-graphics-cards-market</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.digitimes.com/news/a20180307PD206.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitimes.com%2Fnews%2Fa20180307PD206.html&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtT